docs.text:
The Roblox OpenSource Initiative
¶


A project dedicated to collecting, indexing, and organizing ROBLOX development tools, resources, and libraries.


Submissions
¶


You can submit a library for review through either through our 
Community Discord
 or via a pull request to our 
GitHub repository
. For more information, see our 
submissions
 page.
